        "kind": "memory",
        "front": "请写出以下函数在x=0处的泰勒展开式: 1. e^x 2. sinx 3. cosx 4. arctanx 5. arcsinx 6. ln(1+x) 7. tanx 8. (1+x)^a",
        "back": "1. e^x = 1 + x + x^2/2! + x^3/3! + o(x^3) 2. sinx = x - x^3/3! + o(x^3) 3. cosx = 1 - x^2/2! + x^4/4! + o(x^4) 4. arctanx = x - x^3/3 + o(x^3) 5. arcsinx = x + x^3/3! + o(x^3) 6. ln(1+x) = x - x^2/2 + x^3/3 + o(x^3) 7. tanx = x + x^3/3 + o(x^3) 8. (1+x)^a = 1 + ax + a(a-1)x^2/2! + o(x^2)",
